The paper deals with the expressive power and learning algorithms of recurrent neural networks, which are typically studied in the machine learning and artificial intelligence communities (cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.NE, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the connection between weighted finite automata and recurrent neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the systems and control community (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.NE, cs.AI, and cs.SY.
